      "timeoriginalestimate": null,
      "description": "\n\n<p>In the Evals → Pipeline Health section, the pipeline status is showing as failed due to LLM credential resolution issues. The system is unable to identify or load an LLM model for the configured tenant.</p>\n\n<p><b>Error Message:</b></p>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li>“LLM credential resolution failed: No LLM model available for tenant.”</li>\n\t<li>“Could not verify provider/key match (credential resolution failed).”</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n<p><b>Actual Result:</b></p>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li>Pipeline Health status shows “Overall: Failed”.</li>\n\t<li>LLM credentials validation is failing.</li>\n\t<li>Judge model/provider configuration is not getting resolved.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n<p><b>Expected Result:</b></p>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li>Valid LLM model should be detected for the tenant.</li>\n\t<li>Provider/key validation should complete successfully.</li>\n\t<li>Pipeline Health status should display as successful when configuration is valid.</li>\n</ul>\n",
